'''Mohamed Hefzy''' (yavutse ku ya 13 Werurwe 1975), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo mu Misiri akaba Umwanditsi . <ref name="screendaily">https://www.screendaily.com/features/the-centrepiece-interview-cairo-chief-mohamed-hefzy-talks-indie-cinema-upcoming-projects/5144584.article</ref> <ref>https://www.enigma-mag.com/mohamed-hefzy/</ref> Umwe mu batunganya amafilime akomeye mu burasirazuba bwo hagati no muri Afurika, Screen International yamwise umwarabu wenyine mu bayobozi 30 bazaza mu gutunganya amafilime mu 2013. Muri 2016, Hefzy yatoranijwe na Variety hejuru yurutonde rw "Amazina icumi ugomba kumenya mu nganda zamafirime y’abarabu" maze amushyira muri Variety 500. <ref>https://variety.com/exec/mohamed-hefzy/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 13 Werurwe 1975 i Cairo mu Misiri . Mbere yo kwinjira muri sinema, yize ibijyanye na metallurgical engineering i Londres. <ref name="cineuropa">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://cineuropa.org/en/filmography/212568/ "Mohamed Hefzy"]. cineuropa<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">8 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Niwe washinze isosiyete ikora 'Film Clinic' iherereye mu Misiri yashinzwe mu 2005.  Binyuze muri iyo sosiyete, yatanze amahugurwa na gahunda zamahugurwa kubantu ba firime yabarabu nabanyafurika bakorana nimiryango mpuzamahanga nibigo. Mu mwaka wa 2010, yabaye umwe mu bagize inteko y'abacamanza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Cairo . Hanyuma mu 2011, yabaye inteko y'abacamanza mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime Abu Dhabi hanyuma aba umunyamuryango mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Venice muri 2018. Kuva mu 2015 kugeza 2017, Hefzy yabaye umuyobozi w'Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Ismailia rya Documentaire na Short, ndetse no mu nama ngishwanama ya Festival mpuzamahanga ya Cairo. Kuva mu 2013, yabaye umwe mu bagize inama y'ubutegetsi ya Sinema yo mu Misiri. <ref name="screendaily" />

Muri 2016, yakoze firime ''Clash'' . Nyuma iyi firime yatoranijwe nka firime itangiza igice cya ' Un Certain Regard ' igice cya Cannes International Festival Festival . Muri 2018, yakoranye na producer ''Yomeddine'' . <ref name="madcelebrity">http://madcelebrity.com/mohamed-hefzy.php</ref> Filime kandi yahisemo kwerekanwa i Cannes mumarushanwa yemewe. Muri 2020, yakoze firime ya ''Luxor'' yitabiriye amarushanwa ya Dramatic World Festival muri Sundance Film Festival . Hagati aho, abo bakoranye, ''Souad, batoranijwe ku'' mugaragaro ku nshuro ya mbere yerekana iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes, ryabaye ku nshuro ya gatatu muri Cannes.  

Muri Werurwe 2018, yabaye perezida muto mu mateka y'iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Cairo, igihe Hefzy yahawe na minisitiri w’umuco. Muri uwo mwaka, yatsindiye Centre ya Arabiya Cinema Centre y’Abarabu Yatanzwe n’Umunyamakuru wa Hollywood kubera uruhare yagize muri sinema yisi. Nyuma muri kamena 2019, yatumiwe nkumunyamuryango wa Academy ya Motions Pictures Arts Arts na Science mu ishami rya "Producer".   <ref name="madcelebrity" />
